<li><strong>Aconitum Napellus: </strong>Aconite is valuable in treating fevers that are closely followed by exposure to cold, during which it addresses <a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/how-to-treat-anxiety-with-homeopathy"   title="anxiety" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked"  data-wpil-monitor-id="2682">anxiety</a> and insomnia caused by high fever.</li>
