<li><strong>Mercurius:</strong> For teary eyes and ears, earache, weak flesh, congested or pained head, and <a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/how-to-treat-toothache-with-homeopathy"   title="toothache" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked"  data-wpil-monitor-id="2288">toothache</a>, better or worse, after eating.</li>



<li><strong>Phytolacca:</strong> Effective when throat pain is felt in the ear, having the sensa­tion of a bruised area and appearing bright red.</li>



<li><strong>Hepar Sulphur:</strong> Approved for severe pain with throat tickles and intense pain with touch or cold air.</li>



<li>Rhus Toxicodendron: Most suitable for a sore throat occasioned by strain in voice usage or weather changes eased by hot beverages or heat.</li>



<li><strong><a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://weclinic.in/blog/arsenicum-album-uses"   title="Arsenicum Album" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked"  data-wpil-monitor-id="2289">Arsenicum Album</a>:</strong> Beneficial for burning throat discomfort and the sensation of lumping stuck in the throat that is exacerbated by lying down or when awake and anxious.</li>



<li><strong>Kali Bichromicum:</strong> Especially useful when there is lots of thick caught-up mucus, when one feels like constantly clearing the throat, when there is a sharp pain in the throat, and when there is dryness or irritation felt.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Best Homeopathic Remedies for Sore Throat</h2>



