<li><strong>Arnica Montana:</strong> Recommended for numbness and tingling, inflammation and pain when exercising, or people who confess to being knocked about a bit.</li>



<li><strong>Calcarea Fluorica:</strong> This is for conditions like stiffness and hard bony deposits, especially where there is pressure, like the knee and hip.</li>



